sqlViews.name: user_data_withstartdate
sqlViews.sqlQuery:
SELECT ps.name as stagename, EXTRACT(hour from teidva.created) as hour, teidva.modifiedby as user,
COUNT(teidva.trackedentitydatavalueauditid) as edits 
FROM trackedentitydatavalueaudit as teidva
JOIN programstageinstance as psi on psi.programstageinstanceid = teidva.programstageinstanceid
JOIN programstage as ps on ps.programstageid = psi.programstageid
where teidva.created >= TO_DATE('${startdate}', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND teidva.created <= TO_DATE('${enddate}', 'YYYY-MM-DD') 
GROUP BY (teidva.modifiedby, ps.name, hour)
order by user, stagename, hour asc
